title: [Calelith Villa, Garden]
description: Tall stalks of wheat grow wild, swaying in the breeze like ripples on the sea.  Wildflowers dot the golden sea of wheat, providing stark contrasts of color in the moonlight.  To the north, the forest borders the golden field.
